'''Sweeper storms''' were massive storms created by [[Weather control/Legends|weather control]] machines on [[Bonadan/Legends|Bonadan]]. Extremely violent, they were used to help clean the pollution out of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmosphere]].

